 combat with weapon-specific actions, dodges, guards, parries, and counterattacks.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680330/extras/8d6558c32d8b6f253a3dc52d3b09ff29.poster.avif?t=1757481240\" width=480 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680330/extras/8d6558c32d8b6f253a3dc52d3b09ff29.webm?t=1757481240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680330/extras/8d6558c32d8b6f253a3dc52d3b09ff29.mp4?t=1757481240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Defeat unique devils and bosses!<br>Collect over 190 different items to identify enemy weaknesses and attack strategically.",
